quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Say: “O you Al-Kafirun (Those who disbelieve Al-Kitab)"
  109,2,I do not obey whatever you worship
  109,3,while you are not worshippers to That Whom I pay obedience
  109,4,and I am not obedient to what you worshipped
  109,5,while you are not worshippers to That Whom I pay obedience
  109,6,"To you (be) your way of life; and to me, my Religion (which comes from the Creator)"